{"tid":771931,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一坐旅遊巴就會頭痛","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T12:09:02.000Z","uid":66106,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"216af89b12831265070868fa7dbd9da6b38adb20","tid":771931,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"平時坐巴士，船都完全無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐親旅遊巴一上到去聞到嗰陣旅遊巴味就會開始頭痛，然後暈車浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5e0e92180df2c1c9a937a95d5bfdf546cf51ba","tid":771931,"uid":55346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"Me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3c6f90489362aab3cb5d0200922e13a68b55ba","tid":771931,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"仿皮/絨櫈味"},{"pid":"f7d8070398a1311f5e171bbeb1814942ace4d959","tid":771931,"uid":66106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"而家返工放工都會坐旅遊巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都未返到公司就已經完全失去哂動力做野<br />\n放工已經做到頭痛，上埋架旅遊巴就痛上加痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係見到其他人好似乜事都無咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解得我一個會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8773d4c26f6de9e93dc745c5ae395cd1241d4f3","tid":771931,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba842146365620a4